    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am Kalpana Raghav, who was your student in the Bachelor of tourism class of year 2019. I hope you are doing well. I am writing this letter to seek a letter of reference from you to support my application for the job of customer Relationship executive in The Thomas Cook group of companies.",
        "This is a fabulous position that provides destination knowledge and a great career opportunity for a fresher. Given my flair passion for tourism work and the brand equity of The Thomas cook group in this field, I am eager to get this job.",
